              <span id="reviewTextContainer514305532" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18090526653970332402">Fast, fun, and gritty. The narrative&apos;s scope is too wide to deliver fully on any one of its major story lines. Its episodes deliver a portrait of a city bursting with tension. A great jumping-off point--recommended.</span>
  <span id="freeText18090526653970332402" style="display:none">Fast, fun, and gritty. The narrative's scope is too wide to deliver fully on any one of its major story lines. Its episodes deliver a portrait of a city bursting with tension. A great jumping-off point--recommended.</span>
